Library context menu integration
--------------------------------
src/contextMenuPatch.tsx adds a single entry to the Steam library context menu.
The technique it uses to resolve and patch Steam's internal LibraryContextMenu
class is derived from the decky-steamgriddb plugin by the SteamGridDB project,
which is licensed under the GNU General Public License v3.

